enhanced_by.reason: The compare method relies on the initialization of the Transformer and Comparator objects, which are set up in the constructor.
The compare method's result can be verified by comparing the state of the TransformingComparator object before and after the comparison, similar to how the equals method checks for state equality.
The compare method heavily depends on the Transformer's apply method to transform the input objects before comparison, making it a critical part of the assertion process.
